data.description: PRICE CUT-MOTIVATED SELLER!! SELLER FOUND SUITABLE HOUSING! Water VIEW to the Slack Reservoir! This one-level living property is very attractive to many buyers and will not last long on the market! Offering many extras, including premium vinyl siding, a newer roof and windows with a 50-year warranty, a 5-year-old addition, AC, water softener, premium leaf guard gutters, a new driveway, a fenced-in yard, solar panels with a TESLA power bank and more! Property could also be a great option for an AIR-BNB investment opportunity!
